OL,5, Carol Vorderman is to leave her weekly 
OL,6, show on BBC Radio Wales after breaking 
OL,7, BBC guidelines by attacking the        
OL,8, government on social media.            
OL,10,FThe presenter, who has hosted the      
OL,11,FSaturday morning show for four years,  
OL,12,Fis a vocal critic of the government on 
OL,13,FX, formerly Twitter.                   
OL,15,FThe BBC recently published new social  
OL,16,Fmedia rules for stars and staff.       
OL,18,FVorderman said she was not "prepared to
OL,19,Flose my voice on social media" and     
OL,20,Fmanagers "have decided I must leave".  
